(void)attack.cast:(string)name  Use the name, Fill the context and cast the attack
Process is made with all sorts of events, all events use the attack as a context,
meaning it is available for altering it all along the process :
- Call OnAttackCast on self ; 
- Use of attacks areas to determine targets ; 
- Call OnAttackIsTargeted on target with self as parameter;
And then for each confirmed target, with a specific instance of properties to alter (hence no long-term alteration for those) :
- Call OnAttackHit on self with target as parameter;
- Call OnAttackReceiveHit on target with self as parameter;
- Applies Attack on target using its own logic and properties
